00:29:20.897 --> 00:29:22.519
Bueno, eso es bueno.

00:29:22.657 --> 00:29:24.314
Me dará la oportunidad de explicarme.

00:29:24.452 --> 00:29:26.005
Créeme,

00:29:26.143 --> 00:29:27.524
No les interesa darte nada

00:29:27.662 --> 00:29:29.491
